==Swedish==
===Interjection===
'''pax'''
*[[Wiktionary Appendix:IPA Examples|pronunciation:]] /paks/
#''(children's language)'' [[dibs]] (to claim a stake to something); used as a noun with the verbs ''få'' "get, receive" and ''ha'' "have"
#:'''''Pax''' för soffan!'' - "I have (first) '''dibs''' on the sofa!"
#:''Jag fick '''pax''' på framsätet!'' - "I got '''dibs''' on [[shotgun]]!"

====Etymology====
Since 1880 from latin ''pax'' "peace".

